    long int funct(long int i)//to find sum of that no +its digits
    {
    long int s=0;
    int a,k,l,m,n,o;
    a=i/100000;
k=i/10000-a*10;
    l=i/1000-k*100;
    m=(i/100)-10*l-1000*k;
    n=i/10-m*10-100*l-10000*k;
    o=i-1000*l-100*m-10*n-100000*k;
s=a+k+l+m+n+o+i;


    return s;
    }
